{"tid":1625854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[長文] 究竟要再做咩先可以加速成個運動?","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:18.000Z","uid":39988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a4acf02c621d057ddaf5337790306f1d0f0250d1","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"成個運動都4個月, 要遊行有遊行, 要反抗有反抗, 要勇武有勇武, 要犧牲有犧牲<br />\n家下好明顯球証, 足總, 足協都係佢地既人, 指望佢地會有良知醒覺以經唔太可能<br />\n家下好明顯有2個大方向:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><em><em><ins><ins><strong>1. 加速攬炒</strong></ins></ins></em></em></strong></strong><br />\n一直以黎, 林病都想一舉兩得, 咪撚再遊行反對, 一方面要保撚住香港呢隻生金蛋&quot;金雞&quot;<br />\n<br />\n金融, 低關稅轉口貿易, 旅遊<br />\n特殊關稅, 港美掛鉤<br />\n由頭到尾, 香港優勢同特點都係美國比<br />\n講咩中美貿易令人憂心, 屌啦, 多謝都講唔切, 關香港撚事, 想呃鳩港豬<br />\n<br />\n大家要知道, 睇得出佢地好想保住隻金雞<br />\n一係就自己親手殺金雞, 無晒低關稅 &gt; 轉口貿易可以收檔<br />\n外資大量切走 &gt; 股市唔再有地位, 自由公平<br />\n諗下香港無晒呢3大收入, 重有咩值錢地位, 無文化特點, 無旅遊價值, 無本土生產產物<br />\n中國無得再係香港玩財技, <ins>孟晚舟案:</ins>, 如果法律同自由度比視中國一樣, 有幾多人投資?<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">涉隱瞞用香港殼公司與伊朗交易 孟晚舟望以豪宅、戴電子腳鐐換保釋<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%AD-%E6%B6%89%E7%94%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AE%BC%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-%E5%94%AE%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99-%E7%BE%8E8%E6%9C%88%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D%E6%B1%82%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AE%25BC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8-%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599-%25E7%25BE%258E8%25E6%259C%2588%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25B7%259D%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B8%25A1%2F&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=9fe0b052\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25BA%25AD-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25AE%25BC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8-%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599-%25E7%25BE%258E8%25E6%259C%2588%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%25B7%259D%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B8%25A1%2F&h=3d9a813a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%AD-%E6%B6%89%E7%94%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%AE%BC%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-%E5%94%AE%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99-%E7%BE%8E8%E6%9C%88%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D%E6%B1%82%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1/</a></span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>要攬炒既係要方法殺左香港呢隻&quot;金雞&quot;</ins></strong><br />\n一個月前搞機場係一個好目標<br />\n一直經濟同發聲方向都好應該<ins><strong>向外</strong></ins><br />\n對其他國家宣傳, 搞機場係要香港柒出國際<br />\n<strong><ins>破壞香港國際形象同經濟 搞壞背後經濟同地位先係重點</ins></strong><br />\n香港經濟地位好, 你受惠有幾多? 表面上加人工有追到inflation? 樓價?<br />\n香港經濟好只係落係小數商人同政府 政府最後反手益撚晒新移民同中國, Fing晒錢去九唔搭八地方, 真正回饋市民有幾多? 你自己知<br />\n<br />\n<ins>最後一句:無晒金融同貿易轉口, 香港邊到值錢?</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">【美食博覽2019】航班取消水果滯留福岡 展商：有外地人員拒來港<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/363899/%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F%E5%8D%9A%E8%A6%BD2019-%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%9C%E6%BB%AF%E7%95%99%E7%A6%8F%E5%B2%A1-%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86-%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%92%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F363899%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258D%259A%25E8%25A6%25BD2019-%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%25BB%25AF%25E7%2595%2599%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25B2%25A1-%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%2592%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=5ce5315f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/363899/%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F%E5%8D%9A%E8%A6%BD2019-%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%9C%E6%BB%AF%E7%95%99%E7%A6%8F%E5%B2%A1-%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86-%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%92%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><em>2.加速美國&quot;民主及人權法案&quot; 通過</em></ins></strong><br />\n成個遊戲都已經唔公平, 黑哨, 無球例, 睇落只係得法案有救香港<br />\n家下已經去到一個樽頸位, 法案每日都有加料, 有議員表示支持點點點<br />\n但同時行動已經有可能會令美國產生反感, 做裝修, 燒野食, 呢到係一個好難平衡既位<br />\n最後影響通過速度, 反手可能失人心, 過份破壞發洩, 運動失焦, 不再對準政權軸心<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>究竟我地要做咩行動先可以表達到通法案支持同渴求<br />\n靜坐? 遊行? 上街對戰? 定咩行動先可以表現到?</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n反正家下打又唔夠黑警打茅波, 踢波你又用手, 11人一隊你又踢緊21人, 用炮指撚住你<br />\n每一次交戰都無咩得著, 每次用手足去換核彈, 睇到心痛, 18/22歲好應該打下波溝下女<br />\n點解用自己十年青春換本來已經有既普世價值?<br />\n<br />\n<ins>最後一句: 我地要做咩行動先可以加速到美國對法案通過同支持度</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><em>3.意見反對者重要性</em></strong></ins><br />\n唔該大家用多幾秒去睇去諗清楚每個留言, 唔係反對就係on9<br />\n意見反對者係一種思想同討論中既盲點突破者, 因人係會只接收同自己持相同立場意見<br />\n見唔同立場意見就話人on9 係鬼, 其實佢地係幫緊我地<br />\n只睇到做法好處又唔理會做法既問題, 好可能一個盲點就比人不攻而破<br />\n如果能理解他方思想同做法, 再加以填補及破解反對者意見, 修改做法及內容, 最後先對行動有利<br />\n<br />\n小弟學淺, 理性討論<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c6aa7643d22e6d56a4f4fb642d4ad32fe4280ac7","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fae39b239d6025a45b3cb598a04e9c01b5271162","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:44:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a41a6f72da90e6f80e44fa76d4b60b6788bd9800","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e516fb0aba31181b3cbe04c03046ac571f732c8","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc968006632d33e1e434871cc8ceb5e2ca8dec85","tid":1625854,"uid":131770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e9011e75936f555181fdc2468c930da022d6453","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a2d5ef546c4964ebc76cea382a1f177bdaeded8","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:55:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62a5aea5411f3d09d34ac383cc0a400c5c377b18","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:03:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af20ca02bd31fe6dc2830deabc3b7bf9607e3f7c","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d820bf1b735aed4284ceaa0d5c668c1c728be363","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8510839012273f7071b4a36f88b54e42679ae68d","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:17:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79f05e6c5b333037a98a4e3d2cd43fb55d9eab99","tid":1625854,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"一個月內會過human right act，過左睇埋中共咩反應先再諗應對啦<br />\n依家我地既工作就係繼續示威"},{"pid":"2b390efe0f92b8eb290b602d98d72290bd8dd7c9","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43239750770234f6650948d2807a03b2057122a7","tid":1625854,"uid":39988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7fb7f16cccbea7804f06e91bdf90d0ac8fa59f4","tid":1625854,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"有用post永遠推唔到<br />\n大家幫下小弟手可以嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［緊急幫推］可唔可以搵文宣組即時整18區開花poster<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630136</a>"}]}